ripsync has the following dependencies:

* python audio tools (http://sourceforge.net/projects/audiotools/files/latest/download)
For ripping CDs to mp3:

* cddb-py (http://cddb-py.sourceforge.net/) 
For automatic lookup of artist info, etc:

* boto (pip, https://github.com/boto/boto)
For synchronization to Amazon S3 for backup:

* dbus-python
For listening to hardware (hal) events in linux

